	(property "Description" "Non-dissipative internal and adjustable Over Power Protection (OPP) circuits; Frequency Foldback down to 26 kHz and Skip-Cycle in light load conditions; Frequency jittering from full load to skip-cycle; Rich Set of Integrated Protections: Pre-short, OPP, OVP, OCP, SCP, OTP with AutoRecovery or Latched Options.; Improved IC Power Consumption; Internal Ramp Compensation; High Robustness and High ESD Capabilities"
